nodes.text: OK thanks Person1. It seems my follow up appointment with Dr. Person2 did not get scheduled for tomorrow as I was told. Are you able to help with this only I haven had a response to either my e-mail or a phone message I left? Spoke with his office this morning and they knew nothing about it. All very disconcerting to be honest especially after having seen the biopsy report for myself. Thank you,  Person3
